YELLOW FEVER - BRAZIL (GOIAS)
*****************************
A ProMED-mail post
<http://www.promedmail.org>
See Also
Yellow fever - Brazil (Mato Grosso & Para) 19990326203619
Yellow fever - Brazil (Mato Grosso) 19990316205145
